{"body": "Sorry, to make it clearer, I agree about being consistent throughout the project, and that it'd take time to have the entire codebase converted. But we also have to think that by applying once big change like that, we'd get tons of other big changes to make things consistent *everywhere*, and we can avoid that by not applying cosmetic/general changes. It's better to do it in baby steps.\r\n\r\nBesides that, @rafaelfranca just linked me to a related pull request/comment that I missed, please take a look #7781. \r\n\r\nThanks!", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/10845683", "created_at": "2012-11-29T12:40:06Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8367#issuecomment-10845683", "updated_at": "2012-11-29T12:40:06Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8367, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5